title: [Caffe2] Unable to clone Caffe2 repo
body_html:
command run
git clone --recursive https://github.com/caffe2/caffe2

Checking connectivity... done.
Submodule path 'third_party/zstd': checked out 'aec56a52fbab207fc639a1937d1e708a282edca8'
Unable to checkout 'f3c627d517968c20e8269ead1d90cd3a6c199356' in submodule path 'third_party/aten'

  • Error messages and/or stack traces of the bug
  • Context around what you are trying to do
